                                                    <p>5️⃣ Writing Task 2 (Essay Writing) – Structuring arguments and using advanced vocabulary.</p>
                                                    <p>6️⃣ Speaking Practice & Fluency – Enhancing pronunciation, coherence, and confidence.</p>
